                  "revisionId": 2768981,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Notably, each individual hit of Parazon finisher attacks can trigger the effects of this mod. for example, a 'backstab' finisher on a grineer lancer triggers the effect twice, while a finisher on an ancient healer triggers it four times."
